1263.name: FL 8111
1263.Applications: Sub arc flux suitable for a wide range off applications in offshore and general steelwork, cladding valves, shafts, tanks, steel mill rollers etc.
1263.Suitable_For: Submerged arc welding with stainless steel wires, AISI 410, 410NiMo, 308L, 316L, 2209 duplex, 347, 309L, 309LMo, 308H, super duplex, zeron 100, SAF 2507
